txt.en: Your efforts have truly assisted those who work to secure Umbar for the people. You will certainly be rewarded for your accomplishments.

The Quartermaster has requested your aid in the continued efforts to help the people of Umbar.

'We must assist the people of Umbar!

'I ask for your help to aid in this effort. If you are able to take on the ills of Umbar, and bring justice to our home, we would be most indebted to you.'
